high_descs: Turn left and look at the towel hanging on the ring.
Take the towel from the ring.
Around and walk to the toilet paper roll.
Place the towel on the back of the toilet on the right.
Turn around and walk to the towel on the right side of the mirror.
Take the towel from the ring.
Turn around and walk back to the toilet.
Place the towel on the left side of the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place two towels on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sinks counter.
Take the towel off of the ring on the wall.
Turn right and walk to the end of the sinks counter and then turn right and walk to the side of the shower and to the left of the toilet.
Put the towel on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Take the towel off of the ring on the wall.
Turn around and walk back to where you put the first towel.
Put the towel on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the counter left of the sink.
Remove the towel from the towel ring.
Turn to the right and move to the toilet.
Place the towel on to the toilet tank.
Turn right and move to the counter right of the sink.
Remove the towel from the towel ring.
Turn to the left and move to the toilet.
Place the towel on to the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place two towels onto the top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the hand towel that is to the left of the mirror.
Take the hand towel on the hanger off.
With the hand towel in hand go to the toilet.
Place the hand towel on the back of the toilet to the right of the green spray bottle and in front of the bottle of lotion.
Turn and go to the towel that is hanging on the wall to the right of the mirror.
Pick up the towel that is on the towel holder.
With the towel in hand turn around and go to the toilet.
Place the towel behind the green bottle that is on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move the towels to the back of the toilet.
